35:29.057 --> 35:31.400
That's right.

35:31.540 --> 35:32.100
Same way.

35:32.160 --> 35:33.602
I mean, that's a fair statement?

35:33.622 --> 35:36.144
That's a fair statement.

35:36.164 --> 35:44.933
