She had two of them?

38:11.122 --> 38:16.046
So I said to her, I said, well, here's the story she told me.

38:16.627 --> 38:17.127
She said,

38:17.461 --> 38:21.046
Parker lived in her mother's house in the South.

38:21.066 --> 38:21.567
Wow.

38:21.827 --> 38:28.637
And when this book was published, you know, he gave his, I want his grandmother one, but this one won it.

38:28.857 --> 38:31.320
