38:31.440 --> 38:34.064
And we're talking about a book that's exceedingly skit.

38:34.244 --> 38:40.533
I just saw it, I just saw it, the Christie sale that you went to a couple weeks ago, they had a marble farm.

38:40.713 --> 38:40.934
Yeah.

38:41.074 --> 38:43.377
And I think they got, they got a pretty good price for it.

38:43.537 --> 38:45.460
I forget, it was $13,000, $14,000, I think.

38:46.435 --> 38:51.342
So you see when things happen, you see how she pulled another one, you know?

38:51.362 --> 38:54.887
It was like pulling a rabbit out of a hat.

38:54.907 --> 38:56.229
How long ago is this, roughly?

38:56.529 --> 39:01.796
Oh, this must be 12 years ago, 15 years ago.

39:01.876 --> 39:08.345
And you obviously had clients immediately who would... Oh, yes, I sold them both immediately, the same day as a matter of fact.

39:08.365 --> 39:09.267
Really?

